New Records: Victor Wembanyama scored a career-high 50 points in the San Antonio Spurs' 139-130 win over the Washington Wizards on November 14, 2024.
Key Match Events: Wembanyama's aggressive hunting of the shot, particularly his five 3-point attempts in the first 5.5 minutes, was a turning point in the game. His ability to shoot from deep and drive to the basket created significant offensive momentum for the Spurs.
